  "title": "Supervisor (Coffeeshop)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- To be well-informed in administrative matters of tenants</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- Conduct daily sales and audit checks</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- Provide on-job training and plan duty rosters</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- Ensure the respective outlets to adhere to the hygiene SOP</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- Ensure outlet maintenance</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- Ensure accuracy in inventory stocks check</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- To take note of the customers' preferences and report to Head</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- Minimum 2 years’ relevant experience in F&amp;B industry</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- Processes excellent communication and interpersonal skills</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- Resourceful and ability to work under pressure</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>- PC proficiency in MS Words and Excel</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Duration：8-10 hours / daily</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Immediate start</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits：</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>-Additional Attendance Bonus</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>-Year-End Performance Bonus</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>-Annual Leave / Sick Leave</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>-6 days work week</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>",
